content_raw_data.data:
On June 22, 2021, the reputable Raid Forums actor "TomLiner" posted a thread offering to sell 700 million scraped records from the professional networking platform LinkedIn (linkedin[.]com). The same actor published a similar offering on April 3, 2021. Press releases from LinkedIn on April 8, 2021 and June 29, 2021 note that "this data was scraped from LinkedIn and other various websites" and not sourced from a breach. ZeroFOX acquired the entire database of 700 million records from a sensitive source with direct access. From this package, ZeroFOX extracted 121,578,766 email addresses.
